    "title": "6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<p>Dental implants are a trustworthy and natural-looking way to bring back your smile. More than 3 million Americans have already enjoyed the benefits of dental implants. Before you decide, make sure you're aware of these 6 important points about dental implants.</p>\n<img alt=\"6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img>"
  },
