    "page": 2,
    "title": "6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>1. Check Your Bone Health</h4>\n<p>Your jawbone is crucial for dental implants. When you lose a tooth, the bone starts to shrink. An x-ray will show if your jawbone is healthy and strong enough for implants.</p>\n<img alt=\"6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 3,
    "title": "6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>2. Natural Look and Feel</h4>\n<p>Dental implants mimic natural teeth. The titanium roots fuse with your jawbone, creating a solid base for bridges, dentures, or crowns.</p>\n<img alt=\"6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants_3\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_3.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_3.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_3.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_3.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 4,
    "title": "6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>3. Pain-Free Procedure</h4>\n<p>Don't worry about pain. Local anesthesia makes the implant surgery comfortable. Surgical guides ensure precision and minimal discomfort.</p>\n<img alt=\"6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants_4\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_4.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_4.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_4.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_4.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\"><br/>\n\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 5,
    "title": "6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>4. Be Ready to Commit Time</h4>\n<p>Getting dental implants is a long-term process. From consultation to final restoration, it can take up to a year. Be prepared for multiple visits and healing periods.</p>\n<img alt=\"6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants_5\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_5.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_5.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_5.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_5.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\"><br/>\n\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 6,
    "title": "6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>5. Maintain Your Implants</h4>\n<p>While implants resist gum disease, they aren't immune. Bacteria can still cause issues. Brush twice a day and floss regularly to keep your implants healthy.</p>\n<img alt=\"6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants_6\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_6.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_6.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_6.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_6.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 7,
    "title": "6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants",
    "article": "\n<h4>6. Long-Term Investment</h4>\n<p>With proper care, dental implants can last a lifetime. Choose an experienced prosthodontist and maintain good oral hygiene to protect your investment.</p>\n<img alt=\"6 Must-Knows About Dental Implants_7\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_7.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_7.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_7.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants/6-must-knows-about-dental-implants_7.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img>"
